%A1ng/poem-U5ONJ7CzzmxBKR9zV4LdOQ">Tống Đàm hiệu uý quy Quế Dương - 送譚校尉歸桂陽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Trung-thu-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Quan-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-AEC6I0cqYu-k5cNGd4tJCw">Trung thu dạ Đại Quan viên tức cảnh - 中秋夜大觀園即景</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-li%C3%AAn-c%C3%BA-ng%C5%A9-ng%C3%B4n-b%C3%A0i-lu%E1%BA%ADt-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7-h%E1%BA%A1n-nh%E1%BB%8B-ti%C3%AAu-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-wMQlYGlF6aUupM2pBicmdQ">Tức cảnh liên cú ngũ ngôn bài luật nhất thủ, hạn “nhị tiêu” vận - 即景聯句五言排律一首，限二蕭韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-tr%E1%BA%A7n/poem--MNivfmhfmKdaENtm576XQ">Xuất trần - 出塵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
